title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
description: When attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: When trying to export data from a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Insert a table inside one of the cells.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Observe the exception that is thrown.
